old guard communists has become the longestserving leader in the 
soviet bloc 
ceausescus crash industrialization program and the domestic 
austerity he imposed to repay romanias 11 billion foreign debt 
have caused widespread shortages and food rationing the pervasive 
and feared secret police are the main agency used to keep the 
people under control 
mihnea berindei vice chairman of the parisbased romanian 
